<section id="pc-pay">
  <div id="pc-payment">
    <h4>How To Pay</h4>
    <hr>
    <p>Its easy to pay for your products at Love Jeans And T-shirts. There are two ways to do so, both of which are very safe. You can pay for your purchases via this website directly, by using the shopping cart and checkout. Here you add the products you would like to purchase to the shopping cart. After this you proceed to the checkout page, where you then select pay pal as the payment method. This will take you to the pay pal page where you will be asked to enter your credit card details and confirm payment. You will then receive an email confirming your purchase.</p><br>
    <p>Alternatively, if you are not comfortable paying using pay pal, please contact us to arrange a bank transfer. You can contact us at our Facebook page by clicking the link at the top of the Home page. Also, feel free to contact us vis Line or phone us. Our Line ID and mobile number can be found at the top of the home page also.</p>
  </div>
</section>
